comments: Porzingis (WAS) establishes himself in Christie's (LAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Christie (LAL) is moving alongside Beal's (WAS) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Bryant (LAL) avoids making contact with Gafford's (WAS) arm during his shot attempt near the rim.
Gafford (WAS) establishes himself in Christie's (LAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Christie (LAL) puts his arms into a vertical position as he moves alongside Beal's (WAS) path and avoids making arm contact during his driving shot attempt.
Bryant (LAL) and Beal (WAS) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Walker IV (LAL) reaches in and incidental hand on ball contact occurs with Gafford (WAS) prior to his upward shooting motion.
James (LAL) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Bryant (LAL) establishes himself and firms up over his left foot in Kuzma's (WAS) path and marginal contact occurs as Kuzma navigates over the pick.
Christie (LAL) is moving alongside Beal's (WAS) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Walker IV (LAL) initiates contact with Beal's (WAS) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) makes incidental contact with the ball and his knee.
After the ball becomes loose, James (LAL) and Avdija (WAS) mutually engage and marginal contact occurs as they come together.
James (LAL) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
